[Civil No. 769.] A. REDEWILL, Appellant, v. C. W. STEVENS, Appellee. APPEAL from the District Court of the Third Judicial District. J. L. B. Alexander, and G. P. Bullard, Attorneys for Appellee. January 28, 1902.

No appearance for Appellant.

Affirmed on short transcript under par. 1583, Rev. Stats. Ariz. 1901.
